-- One in Every Two German Voters Want Deutsche Mark Back, Bild Zeitung Says
-- Brian Parkin
-- 2010-06-30T06:21:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/one-in-every-two-german-voters-want-deutsche-mark-back-bild-zeitung-says.html

          
          
             Just over half of German voters, 51
percent, would prefer a return to the deutsche mark, while 30
percent favor sticking with the euro, the  Bild Zeitung  reported,
citing a poll by market researcher Ipsos.  
 The newspaper provided no further details about the poll.  
